-- Goldcorp Says Guatemala to Start Marlin Probe, Mine to Continue Operating
-- Simon Casey
-- 2010-06-24T11:17:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-24/goldcorp-says-guatemala-to-start-marlin-probe-mine-to-continue-operating.html

          
          
             Goldcorp Inc. said the Guatemalan
government initiated a process to further investigate
allegations of pollution caused by its Marlin mine.  
 The company expects “normal operations” at Marlin while
the process in under way, Goldcorp said today in a Marketwire
statement.  
